<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>Order Confirmation - NextMart</title>
   <style>
      body {
         font-family: 'Outfit', 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
         background-color: #0b0f19;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 0;
         color: #e2e8f0;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
         max-width: 600px;
         margin: 30px auto;
         background-color: #111827;
         border-radius: 16px;
         overflow: hidden;
         box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
         border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      }
      .header {
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f52ba, #1e3a8a);
         padding: 40px 30px;
         text-align: center;
         color: #ffffff;
      }
      .logo {
         max-height: 48px;
         margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .header h2 {
         margin: 0;
         font-size: 26px;
         font-weight: 700;
         letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }
      .content {
         padding: 40px 30px;
         line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .content h1 {
         color: #60a5fa;
         font-size: 22px;
         margin-top: 0;
         font-weight: 600;
      }
      .order-meta {
         font-size: 14px;
         color: #9ca3af;
         margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      .items-table {
         width: 100%;
         border-collapse: collapse;
         margin: 25px 0;
      }
      .items-table th {
         text-align: left;
         padding: 12px 10px;
         border-bottom: 2px solid #374151;
         color: #9ca3af;
         font-weight: 600;
         font-size: 13px;
         text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .items-table td {
         padding: 16px 10px;
         border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937;
         color: #f3f4f6;
         font-size: 15px;
      }
      .summary-table {
         width: 100%;
         border-collapse: collapse;
         margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .summary-table td {
         padding: 6px 10px;
         font-size: 15px;
      }
      .summary-table td.label {
         color: #9ca3af;
         text-align: right;
      }
      .summary-table td.value {
         color: #f3f4f6;
         text-align: right;
         font-weight: 500;
         width: 120px;
      }
      .summary-table tr.total-row td {
         border-top: 2px solid #374151;
         padding-top: 12px;
         font-weight: 700;
         font-size: 18px;
      }
      .summary-table tr.total-row td.value {
         color: #60a5fa;
      }
      .address-box {
         background-color: #1f2937;
         padding: 20px;
         border-radius: 8px;
         margin: 25px 0;
         border: 1px solid #374151;
      }
      .address-box h3 {
         margin-top: 0;
         margin-bottom: 10px;
         font-size: 15px;
         color: #60a5fa;
         text-transform: uppercase;
         letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      .address-box p {
         margin: 0;
         font-size: 14px;
         color: #e2e8f0;
      }
      .cta-button {
         display: block;
         background-color: #3b82f6;
         color: #ffffff !important;
         text-decoration: none;
         padding: 14px 30px;
         font-size: 16px;
         font-weight: 600;
         border-radius: 8px;
         margin: 30px auto;
         text-align: center;
         box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
         max-width: 220px;
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .footer {
         background-color: #0d131f;
         padding: 25px 30px;
         text-align: center;
         font-size: 13px;
         color: #6b7280;
         border-top: 1px solid #1f2937;
      }
      .footer a {
         color: #3b82f6;
         text-decoration: none;
         font-weight: 500;
      }
   </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="header">
         <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dbgrq28js/image/upload/v1736763971/logoipsum-282_ilqjfb_paw4if.png" alt="NextMart Logo" />
         <h2>Order Confirmed!</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
         <h1>Thank you for your order, {{userName}}!</h1>
         <p class="order-meta">Order ID: <strong>#{{orderId}}</strong><br>Date: {{orderDate}}</p>
         
         <p>Your order has been received and is currently being processed. We have attached a copy of your invoice for your records.</p>
         
         <table class="items-table">
            <thead>
               <tr>
                  <th>Product</th>
                  <th style="text-align: center;">Qty</th>
                  <th style="text-align: right;">Price</th>
               </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
               {{#each products}}
               <tr>
                  <td>{{this.product.name}} {{#if this.color}}({{this.color}}){{/if}}</td>
                  <td style="text-align: center;">{{this.quantity}}</td>
                  <td style="text-align: right;">${{this.unitPrice}}</td>
               </tr>
               {{/each}}
            </tbody>
         </table>

         <table class="summary-table">
            <tr>
               <td class="label">Subtotal</td>
               <td class="value">${{totalAmount}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{#if discount}}
            <tr>
               <td class="label">Discount</td>
               <td class="value">-${{discount}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/if}}
            <tr>
               <td class="label">Delivery Charge</td>
               <td class="value">${{deliveryCharge}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="total-row">
               <td class="label">Total Amount</td>
               <td class="value">${{finalAmount}}</td>
            </tr>
         </table>

         <div class="address-box">
            <h3>Shipping Address</h3>
            <p>{{shippingAddress}}</p>
         </div>

         <a href="https://next-mart-client-sable.vercel.app/dashboard/my-orders" class="cta-button">Track Your Order</a>

         <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes to your order, feel free to reply directly to this email or contact support at support@nextmart.com.</p>
         <p>Happy Shopping!<br><strong>The NextMart Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
         <p>© 2026 NextMart Ltd. Level-4, 34, Awal Centre, Banani, Dhaka.</p>
         <p>You received this email because you made a purchase at NextMart. If you believe this is an error, please contact us.</p>
      </div>
   </div>
</body>
</html>
